f I where to sell some of my items what would  I sell and what should I get to replace it? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uhaganwood.showPublicProfile?language=EN>haganwood</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk</span><br>  Posts: 108<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(8/6/02 6:56:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10759.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sell some stuff and get tstaff or stick with 1hb?</span><hr size=1> I would stick with what you have till you get a better 2HB skill and go camp in KC at H/WL and get your own Tstaff, also to get 2HB skill up you could get a Bamboo Bo out of Dalnir 8/20 and use it on raids that you really don't have to do a ton of damage on.  <br><br>Thats what I did, don't have T-staff myself and not planning on getting one as I like my H2H weapons and my H2H is at 236 at 53 so not really that far behind my 1HB, and my 2HB is lagging a touch at 210.<br><br>Just my thoughts <p>Rukekak Thunderclaw 51st Iksar Disciple Soulbound On Mith Marr  <br> Haganwood Soulsaver 55th Preserver Soulbound On Mith Marr <br> Kilamana Thunderblade 29th Warrior <br>   Nanelan 29th DE necro </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uugle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ugle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(8/6/02 8:28:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10759.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://ugleduklin.tripod.com/sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderpictures/dscn0011s.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title